title: DNSK - Fabian! Birthday Party Set 2015 (The Warmup Mix)
description:
DNSK - Fabian! Birthday Party Set 2015 (The Warmup Mix)


This set was broadcasted on LyfeRadio.com December 21th 2015,
when DJ Fabian had his birthday party at the LyfeRadio studio.

It's an opening act so the style and tempo is dynamic, and evolves with time. 
First out is short mixes of glitch hop, to turn to house, and end in hard bass and hardstyle.


01. Intro - Hit That Jive, Fabian!
